Taiwan Hocheng Jan - Aug sales down . Taiwan ' s largest sanitary - ware maker Hocheng Corp . said on Thursday its combined sales revenue between January and August fell 23 . 42 percent to T $ 3 . 181 billion from T $ 4 . 154 billion in the same period a year earlier . In the month of August , Hocheng ' s sales were T $ 370 million , down 28 . 02 percent year on year , a company statement said . The company did not give reasons for the falls , and profit figures were not available in the statement . - - Taipei Newsroom ( 2 - 5080815 ) 
